name: Disaster Doodle #2
description: Artist: Laura Rafferty - Medium: Traditional Mixed Media in my 4" x 4" Watercolor sketchbook - Year: 2020 - Description: The second attempt at a disaster doodle was intentional. This time I washed a random blob of my favorite colors and dropped my sketchbook. I let it dry, and then repeated the process, dropping it in a closely symmetrical movement. This created a fun blot that I turned into the painting you see!
